entries.femaleVariant: Spell book. Ya got it?
Here for the spell book.
I do, indeed. Tucked away somewhere safe.
You want coordinates? I need to see my money.
Damn, this stinks to high hell... But OK, take you at your word.
entries.maleVariant: Damn, this stinks to high hell... But OK, I'll take you at your word.

entries.femaleVariant: Ouch. Hard Wire customer service just ain't what it used to be...
Huh? I have no idea what you're talkin' about.
Sure you do. Got a pretty good idea of who you are. Bargain basement dress suit, back alley implants – you are almost a cut-out from a corp recruiting brochure.
entries.maleVariant: Sure you do. I got a pretty good idea of who you are. Bargain basement dress suit, back alley implants – you're almost a cut-out from a corp recruiting brochure.

entries.femaleVariant: Just flicked you the coordinates.
Mhm. We'll see.
Uh, yeah?
Whatever.
Never mind.
Look, I have no idea who you are, friend, but this won't do, oh no, no, no, no, no.
I don't like this at all.
[Pay] Fine.
This your attempt at a con?
Wow, service here at Hard Wire's shit these days…
You won't regret it.
Better not. Or you will, bigly. Givin' you my word on that.
Are you trying to fuck me?
No deal. Keep it.
No, not at all, I just--
'Cause I really got it in for people who try that.
Always tempted to end any conversation like that. Violently. Abruptly.
You'd be making a mistake. A big one. I'm not out to con you.
Also... I'm not a victim. I'm prepared just as well as you are.
[Pay] So be it. Take you at your word.
Conversation's over.
Not about to do any biz with a petty con.
And you'd do good to avoid me, all the time, everywhere.
entries.maleVariant: You'd do good to avoid me, all the time, everywhere.

entries.femaleVariant: Hang on, this is fun, lemme guess... Uh, found something in a dusty corner of the warehouse, tryna hawk it off on the side.
entries.maleVariant: Hang on, this is fun, lemme guess... Found somethin' in a dusty corner of the warehouse, tryna hawk it off on the side.

entries.femaleVariant: Agh... what would your manager say? I mean, not like your KPIs can include your under-the-counter deals.
entries.maleVariant: Oooh... what would your manager say? I mean, not like your KPIs can include your under-the-counter deals.

entries.femaleVariant: Ugh, the fuck you want?!
[Pay] Want you to not do anything stupid.
[Negotiate] Discounts. Huge discounts.
Want you to chill, not make any gonk moves.
I'll pay you – but if this isn't worth my while, if it's a con by just a hair… I'll crush you. Got it?
Yes. And fuck you again.
Discount. Somethin' real. Keep me from callin' your boss.
entries.maleVariant: Discount. Somethin' real. Keep me from calling your boss.

entries.femaleVariant: Get fucked, scopshitter.
What the hell is this?!
Oh! Mistake! Big fucking mistake!
Great – got that out of your system, now let's get down to biz. We got a deal, or do I gotta make some calls?
entries.maleVariant: Great – now you got that out of your system, let's get down to biz. We got a deal, or do I gotta make some calls?

entries.femaleVariant: Wow, service here at Hard Wire's shit these days…
